text: Joanne Marie Franks-Edens is an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 1 October 1967. Franks competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics.Joanne Franks-Edens == References == Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain Category:Sportspeople from Norfolk Category:People from King's Lynn
